-TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3,\"repo\":\"jkga/is-web-monetized\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A very simple tool for checking if Web Monetization is enabled.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-07-03T20:00:59.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Tools</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sorxrob/paytrackr\">Paytrackr</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sorxrob/paytrackr\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":7,\"repo\":\"sorxrob/paytrackr\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Track and manage your micropayments into one place.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PayTrackr is the easiest and safest way to track and manage your micropayments to web monetized websites, having a web monetization provider membership.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-07-03T20:00:59.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Tools</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/signalnerve/openmonetizationwallet\">Open Monetization Wallet</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/signalnerve/openmonetizationwallet\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":12,\"repo\":\"signalnerve/openmonetizationwallet\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Tools for managing your vanity Web Monetization wallet.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Open Monetization Wallet (OMW) makes it easier to accept payments with the Web Monetization API at scale. Some features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Custom wallet URLs: own your own \"Payment Pointer\", e.g. $wallet.signalnerve.com, instead of $pay.stronghold.co/abcdef123</li>\n<li>Change between wallets/providers with no downtime</li>\n<li>Logs of incoming payment requests</li>\n<li>Revenue sharing between multiple wallets, e.g. for multiple team members</li>\n<li>Infinitely scalable with serverless technology</li>\n<li>Free and open-source</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-07-03T20:00:59.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Packages</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dacioromero/types-wm\">types-wm</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dacioromero/types-wm\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2,\"repo\":\"dacioromero/types-wm\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - TypeScript definitions for Web Monetization <img src=\"https://github.com/thomasbnt/awesome-web-monetization/raw/main/assets/small_icons/typescript.png\" al